{"id":6162,"date":"2025-09-11T09:13:03","date_gmt":"2025-09-11T06:13:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/?page_id=6162"},"modified":"2025-09-11T16:12:22","modified_gmt":"2025-09-11T13:12:22","slug":"email-marketing-automation-services-in-kenya","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/email-marketing-automation-services-in-kenya\/","title":{"rendered":"Email Marketing &#038; Automation Services in Kenya"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; type=&#8221;vc_default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;5&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;10&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716548610536{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-391695ec204ace08\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-391695ec204ace08 uvc-806 \" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-391695ec204ace08 h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:44px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:54px;\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:45px;\">Email Marketing &amp; Automation Services in Kenya \u2013 Nurture Leads, Drive Sales, and Build Loyalty<\/h2><\/div><\/div>[vc_single_image image=&#8221;6172&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; lazy_loading=&#8221;true&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"98\" data-end=\"140\">Why Email Marketing Still Works in 2025<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"142\" data-end=\"610\">Despite the rise of social media, influencer platforms, and messaging apps, email remains one of the most cost-effective and reliable marketing channels. Global research shows that email marketing generates an average return of <strong data-start=\"370\" data-end=\"396\">$36 for every $1 spent<\/strong>, making it one of the highest ROI digital tactics available. For businesses in Kenya\u2014whether SMEs, corporates, NGOs, or e-commerce brands\u2014this figure highlights why ignoring email means leaving money on the table.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"612\" data-end=\"639\">A Direct, Owned Channel<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"640\" data-end=\"1003\">Unlike social media, where algorithms dictate what your audience sees, email allows you to own the channel. Once someone subscribes, you have direct access to their inbox. This independence from platform changes ensures that your message gets delivered consistently. For businesses operating in Kenya\u2019s competitive digital landscape, this ownership is invaluable.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1005\" data-end=\"1035\">Personal, One-to-One Reach<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1036\" data-end=\"1378\">Email delivers messages straight to a person\u2019s inbox, not a crowded newsfeed. This creates a more personal connection with customers, donors, or stakeholders. Whether it\u2019s an abandoned cart reminder for an e-commerce shopper, a corporate newsletter update, or an NGO impact story, email ensures you reach people in the space they check daily.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1380\" data-end=\"1417\">Scalability Across Business Types<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1418\" data-end=\"1493\">Email marketing scales well across different business sizes and industries:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1494\" data-end=\"1766\">\n<li data-start=\"1494\" data-end=\"1562\">\n<p data-start=\"1496\" data-end=\"1562\"><strong data-start=\"1496\" data-end=\"1504\">SMEs<\/strong> can use email to stay top-of-mind without heavy ad spend.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1563\" data-end=\"1640\">\n<p data-start=\"1565\" data-end=\"1640\"><strong data-start=\"1565\" data-end=\"1579\">Corporates<\/strong> can maintain structured internal and external communication.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1641\" data-end=\"1691\">\n<p data-start=\"1643\" data-end=\"1691\"><strong data-start=\"1643\" data-end=\"1651\">NGOs<\/strong> can engage donors and report on impact.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1692\" data-end=\"1766\">\n<p data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1766\"><strong data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1715\">E-commerce brands<\/strong> can run automated flows that recover revenue 24\/7.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1768\" data-end=\"1798\">Why This Matters for Kenya<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"2224\">Internet penetration in Kenya is at <strong data-start=\"1835\" data-end=\"1860\">over 40 million users<\/strong> (CAK, 2024), with a large percentage accessing email through mobile. With mobile-friendly campaigns and automation tools, businesses can engage audiences at scale, cost-effectively, and with measurable results. While social ads or influencer posts may rise and fall in effectiveness, email marketing remains a proven, adaptable, and revenue-driving channel in 2025.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"54\">Challenges Businesses Face Without Email Automation<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"56\" data-end=\"328\">Many Kenyan businesses recognise the potential of email marketing but fall short when they fail to adopt automation. Without it, campaigns become generic, time-consuming, and ineffective\u2014leading to missed revenue and disengaged audiences. Here\u2019s what typically goes wrong:<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"330\" data-end=\"370\">Generic, One-Size-Fits-All Campaigns<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"371\" data-end=\"751\">SMEs often send the same email blast to their entire database, regardless of audience differences. For example, a Nairobi-based SME selling home appliances might email the same \u201c10% discount\u201d message to loyal customers and first-time leads. The result? Loyal customers ignore it because it feels impersonal, and new leads fail to engage because they need nurturing, not discounts.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"753\" data-end=\"777\">Lack of Segmentation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"778\" data-end=\"1232\">Without segmenting by behaviour, interests, or demographics, open rates and click-throughs remain low. Take an NGO as an example: if donor updates are sent without distinguishing between one-time givers and recurring donors, the message misses relevance. A loyal monthly donor expects impact stories and updates, while a new donor may need reassurance about how their first contribution is making a difference. Without segmentation, both groups tune out.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1234\" data-end=\"1274\">Wasted Leads That Never Get Nurtured<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1275\" data-end=\"1649\">E-commerce businesses in Kenya frequently see abandoned carts\u2014potential buyers who stop just before purchase. Without automated abandoned cart recovery emails, these opportunities vanish. A local fashion e-commerce store could lose thousands of shillings weekly simply because no follow-up email reminds the shopper of their cart or offers an incentive to complete checkout.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1651\" data-end=\"1696\">Manual Processes That Slow Down Campaigns<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1697\" data-end=\"2060\">Manual campaign creation eats into resources. For corporates or NGOs with multiple stakeholders, the approval cycle alone can delay launches by weeks. A training business, for instance, might want to send event reminders and registration confirmations. Doing this manually not only risks errors but also means messages go out too late to drive maximum attendance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2062\" data-end=\"2083\">Poor ROI Tracking<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2084\" data-end=\"2368\">Without automation, businesses struggle to track key metrics like conversion rates or revenue attribution. A Kenyan retailer might know emails are going out but have no idea whether they drive actual sales. This blind spot means decision-making is based on guesswork rather than data.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Need to Email Marketing and Automation Services?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Reach out to us today.[\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"59\">What Our Email Marketing &amp; Automation Services Include<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"61\" data-end=\"317\">Our approach goes beyond simply \u201csending emails.\u201d We design and implement a structured email marketing system that aligns with your business goals, speaks directly to your audience, and delivers measurable results. Here\u2019s what\u2019s included in our services:<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"319\" data-end=\"345\">Strategy Development<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"346\" data-end=\"569\">A successful campaign begins with a clear strategy. We work with you to align email marketing with your broader business objectives\u2014whether that\u2019s increasing online sales, boosting donor retention, or nurturing B2B leads.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"1130\">\n<li data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"901\">\n<p data-start=\"573\" data-end=\"901\"><strong data-start=\"573\" data-end=\"598\">Audience segmentation<\/strong>: We categorise subscribers based on demographics (age, location, income), behaviour (purchase history, browsing activity), and interests. For example, a Kenyan e-commerce brand can segment frequent buyers to receive VIP promotions, while first-time subscribers get educational content about products.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"1130\">\n<p data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"1130\"><strong data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"920\">Defined KPIs<\/strong>: We track metrics such as open rates, click-through rates (CTR), conversions, and ROI. A Nairobi-based training institute might focus on sign-ups per campaign, while an NGO prioritises donor retention rates.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1167\">Campaign Design &amp; Copywriting<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1168\" data-end=\"1305\">Emails that look good and read well convert better. Our creative team builds professional, branded templates tailored to your business.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1841\">\n<li data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1483\">\n<p data-start=\"1309\" data-end=\"1483\"><strong data-start=\"1309\" data-end=\"1336\">Optimised subject lines<\/strong>: Catchy but relevant subject lines drive higher open rates. For instance, \u201cDon\u2019t Miss Out: Your Free Certificate Awaits\u201d for a webinar business.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1484\" data-end=\"1617\">\n<p data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1617\"><strong data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1512\">Persuasive copywriting<\/strong>: Every line is written to move readers towards action\u2014whether that\u2019s donating, buying, or registering.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1618\" data-end=\"1841\">\n<p data-start=\"1620\" data-end=\"1841\"><strong data-start=\"1620\" data-end=\"1639\">Personalisation<\/strong>: Using names, product recommendations, and behavioural data, we ensure every email feels relevant. For example, a Kisumu-based retailer can send \u201cHi James, your preferred trainers are back in stock.\u201d<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1843\" data-end=\"1865\">Automation Setup<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1866\" data-end=\"1972\">Automation ensures your campaigns run 24\/7, engaging customers without requiring constant manual effort.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1974\" data-end=\"2865\">\n<li data-start=\"1974\" data-end=\"2138\">\n<p data-start=\"1976\" data-end=\"2138\"><strong data-start=\"1976\" data-end=\"1994\">Welcome series<\/strong>: New subscribers receive a tailored introduction to your brand. An NGO can use this to show impact stories and encourage recurring donations.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2139\" data-end=\"2321\">\n<p data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2321\"><strong data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2168\">Abandoned cart recovery<\/strong>: For e-commerce brands, automated reminders recover lost revenue. Kenyan online stores typically recover 10\u201320% of abandoned carts through such flows.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2322\" data-end=\"2534\">\n<p data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2534\"><strong data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2357\">Lead nurturing drip campaigns<\/strong>: Service businesses can educate prospects over time. For instance, a Nairobi accounting firm might run a 5-email series explaining how their services reduce compliance risks.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2535\" data-end=\"2708\">\n<p data-start=\"2537\" data-end=\"2708\"><strong data-start=\"2537\" data-end=\"2560\">Re-engagement flows<\/strong>: Dormant subscribers are reactivated with targeted content. Example: A travel agency can re-engage inactive users with seasonal holiday packages.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2709\" data-end=\"2865\">\n<p data-start=\"2711\" data-end=\"2865\"><strong data-start=\"2711\" data-end=\"2746\">Birthday and anniversary emails<\/strong>: Personalised greetings build loyalty and drive additional sales (e.g., discounts on birthdays for loyal customers).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2867\" data-end=\"2897\">List Management &amp; Growth<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2898\" data-end=\"2968\">An effective email strategy depends on a high-quality, growing list.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2970\" data-end=\"3511\">\n<li data-start=\"2970\" data-end=\"3192\">\n<p data-start=\"2972\" data-end=\"3192\"><strong data-start=\"2972\" data-end=\"3005\">Opt-in forms and lead magnets<\/strong>: We create engaging signup opportunities, such as free e-books, discount vouchers, or reports. A Kenyan fitness brand could offer a free 7-day meal plan in exchange for email sign-ups.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3193\" data-end=\"3326\">\n<p data-start=\"3195\" data-end=\"3326\"><strong data-start=\"3195\" data-end=\"3240\">GDPR and Kenya Data Protection compliance<\/strong>: Subscribers\u2019 privacy is respected and protected, giving your business credibility.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3327\" data-end=\"3511\">\n<p data-start=\"3329\" data-end=\"3511\"><strong data-start=\"3329\" data-end=\"3346\">List cleaning<\/strong>: We remove inactive or invalid contacts to improve deliverability. For example, a corporate firm sending HR updates ensures emails don\u2019t bounce or end up in spam.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"3513\" data-end=\"3541\">Testing &amp; Optimisation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3542\" data-end=\"3644\">Email marketing should never be static. We use testing to improve campaign performance continuously.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3646\" data-end=\"4090\">\n<li data-start=\"3646\" data-end=\"3862\">\n<p data-start=\"3648\" data-end=\"3862\"><strong data-start=\"3648\" data-end=\"3663\">A\/B testing<\/strong>: Subject lines, CTAs, send times, and visuals are tested for maximum impact. For instance, a Nairobi e-commerce shop might test \u201c20% Off Today Only\u201d versus \u201cYour Exclusive Discount Ends Midnight.\u201d<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3863\" data-end=\"3957\">\n<p data-start=\"3865\" data-end=\"3957\"><strong data-start=\"3865\" data-end=\"3895\">Content and design testing<\/strong>: We measure what visuals and layouts drive the most clicks.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3958\" data-end=\"4090\">\n<p data-start=\"3960\" data-end=\"4090\"><strong data-start=\"3960\" data-end=\"3984\">Behavioural triggers<\/strong>: Emails are sent based on subscriber actions (e.g., downloading a brochure triggers a follow-up email).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"4092\" data-end=\"4119\">Analytics &amp; Reporting<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4120\" data-end=\"4220\">Data is at the heart of optimisation. We provide detailed analytics so you always know what works.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"4222\" data-end=\"4581\">\n<li data-start=\"4222\" data-end=\"4311\">\n<p data-start=\"4224\" data-end=\"4311\"><strong data-start=\"4224\" data-end=\"4248\">Performance tracking<\/strong>: Open rates, CTR, and conversions are reported in real time.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"4312\" data-end=\"4440\">\n<p data-start=\"4314\" data-end=\"4440\"><strong data-start=\"4314\" data-end=\"4337\">Revenue attribution<\/strong>: For e-commerce brands, we show exactly how much revenue came from each campaign or automation flow.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"4441\" data-end=\"4581\">\n<p data-start=\"4443\" data-end=\"4581\"><strong data-start=\"4443\" data-end=\"4464\">Custom dashboards<\/strong>: Corporates and NGOs get easy-to-read dashboards that show the direct impact of campaigns on organisational goals.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"33\">Email Platforms We Work With<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"35\" data-end=\"322\">Choosing the right email platform is critical for success. Each tool offers different strengths, and the right fit depends on your business model, technical needs, and growth stage. At Aminifu Digital Agency, we help you select and implement the platform that maximises efficiency and ROI.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"324\" data-end=\"339\">Mailchimp<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"340\" data-end=\"567\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mailchimp.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mailchimp<\/a> is one of the most popular email platforms globally and widely used in Kenya. It\u2019s easy to set up, integrates with most websites, and works well for SMEs, NGOs, and businesses just starting out with email marketing.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"569\" data-end=\"824\">\n<li data-start=\"569\" data-end=\"649\">\n<p data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"649\"><strong data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"583\">Best for<\/strong>: Small to mid-sized businesses and NGOs looking for simplicity.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"824\">\n<p data-start=\"652\" data-end=\"824\"><strong data-start=\"652\" data-end=\"670\">Kenyan example<\/strong>: A Nairobi-based non-profit can use Mailchimp to send monthly impact newsletters to donors, while an SME can automate welcome emails for new customers.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"826\" data-end=\"839\">HubSpot<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"1026\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hubspot.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HubSpot<\/a> offers more than just email\u2014it\u2019s a full CRM with automation capabilities. It\u2019s ideal for corporates and B2B service providers that need to align marketing with sales pipelines.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1276\">\n<li data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1133\">\n<p data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1133\"><strong data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1042\">Best for<\/strong>: Corporates, professional services, and organisations with complex lead nurturing needs.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1134\" data-end=\"1276\">\n<p data-start=\"1136\" data-end=\"1276\"><strong data-start=\"1136\" data-end=\"1154\">Kenyan example<\/strong>: A logistics company can use HubSpot to manage client communication, track deals, and automate post-meeting follow-ups.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1298\">ActiveCampaign<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1495\">ActiveCampaign excels in customer journeys and behavioural targeting. It\u2019s strong on segmentation and personalisation, making it a great fit for service businesses and growing e-commerce brands.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1497\" data-end=\"1737\">\n<li data-start=\"1497\" data-end=\"1597\">\n<p data-start=\"1499\" data-end=\"1597\"><strong data-start=\"1499\" data-end=\"1511\">Best for<\/strong>: Businesses ready to move beyond basic newsletters into advanced customer journeys.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1598\" data-end=\"1737\">\n<p data-start=\"1600\" data-end=\"1737\"><strong data-start=\"1600\" data-end=\"1618\">Kenyan example<\/strong>: A training institute can use ActiveCampaign to send drip campaigns that nurture students from enquiry to enrolment.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1739\" data-end=\"1752\">Klaviyo<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1930\">Klaviyo is purpose-built for e-commerce and integrates seamlessly with Shopify and WooCommerce. It\u2019s designed to recover carts, upsell, and track revenue directly from emails.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1932\" data-end=\"2170\">\n<li data-start=\"1932\" data-end=\"1992\">\n<p data-start=\"1934\" data-end=\"1992\"><strong data-start=\"1934\" data-end=\"1946\">Best for<\/strong>: E-commerce brands selling products online.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1993\" data-end=\"2170\">\n<p data-start=\"1995\" data-end=\"2170\"><strong data-start=\"1995\" data-end=\"2013\">Kenyan example<\/strong>: A local fashion store on Shopify can use Klaviyo to trigger abandoned cart reminders, personalised product recommendations, and post-purchase follow-ups.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2172\" data-end=\"2196\">Sendinblue \/ Brevo<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2197\" data-end=\"2397\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.brevo.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Brevo<\/a> (formerly Sendinblue) combines email with SMS marketing, which is highly relevant for Kenyan businesses where SMS penetration is extremely high. It also offers affordable pricing for startups.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2399\" data-end=\"2622\">\n<li data-start=\"2399\" data-end=\"2476\">\n<p data-start=\"2401\" data-end=\"2476\"><strong data-start=\"2401\" data-end=\"2413\">Best for<\/strong>: Businesses that want email + SMS marketing in one platform.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2477\" data-end=\"2622\">\n<p data-start=\"2479\" data-end=\"2622\"><strong data-start=\"2479\" data-end=\"2497\">Kenyan example<\/strong>: A Nairobi events company can use Brevo to send event reminders by email and last-minute SMS alerts for higher attendance.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2624\" data-end=\"2648\">Custom SMTP Setups<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2649\" data-end=\"2845\">For corporates or institutions with strict IT policies, we configure custom SMTP servers to manage bulk email sending directly from their systems. This approach offers full control and security.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2847\" data-end=\"3085\">\n<li data-start=\"2847\" data-end=\"2942\">\n<p data-start=\"2849\" data-end=\"2942\"><strong data-start=\"2849\" data-end=\"2861\">Best for<\/strong>: Banks, government institutions, and enterprises with strict compliance needs.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2943\" data-end=\"3085\">\n<p data-start=\"2945\" data-end=\"3085\"><strong data-start=\"2945\" data-end=\"2963\">Kenyan example<\/strong>: A financial institution can use a custom SMTP setup to send secure client statements and transaction updates directly.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_