ons or seasonal sale reminders. Instead of relying solely on Instagram ads, email provides a direct and owned channel that drives repeat sales at a lower cost.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"783\" data-end=\"807\">Service Businesses<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"808\" data-end=\"1049\">Consultancies, training firms, legal practices, and healthcare providers can use email marketing to nurture leads with educational content. Prospects rarely convert after the first touchpoint, and drip campaigns help build trust over time.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1244\">\n<li data-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1244\">\n<p data-start=\"1053\" data-end=\"1244\"><strong data-start=\"1053\" data-end=\"1064\">Example<\/strong>: A Nairobi accounting firm can run a 5-part email series on compliance tips for SMEs. Each email positions the firm as an expert and leads naturally into a consultation booking.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1246\" data-end=\"1256\">NGOs<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1257\" data-end=\"1436\">For NGOs, email is a cost-effective way to communicate impact, share stories, and drive donations. Donor retention is critical, and segmented campaigns ensure messages resonate.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1438\" data-end=\"1721\">\n<li data-start=\"1438\" data-end=\"1721\">\n<p data-start=\"1440\" data-end=\"1721\"><strong data-start=\"1440\" data-end=\"1451\">Example<\/strong>: A Kenyan NGO focused on education can send success stories to monthly donors while sending first-time donors an onboarding series explaining how contributions are used. Without automation, both groups might receive the same generic appeal\u2014resulting in donor fatigue.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1723\" data-end=\"1739\">Corporates<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1740\" data-end=\"1974\">Corporates use email for both internal and external communications. Externally, newsletters and client updates strengthen relationships. Internally, email can manage structured communication across departments, ensuring consistency.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1976\" data-end=\"2232\">\n<li data-start=\"1976\" data-end=\"2232\">\n<p data-start=\"1978\" data-end=\"2232\"><strong data-start=\"1978\" data-end=\"1989\">Example<\/strong>: A Nairobi-based logistics company can keep clients informed on regulatory updates, case studies, and service expansions through automated newsletters. Internally, HR can send structured updates such as policy changes or training reminders.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2234\" data-end=\"2268\">Events &amp; Training Businesses<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2269\" data-end=\"2497\">Event organisers and training providers benefit greatly from automated workflows. From registration confirmations to reminder emails and post-event follow-ups, automation ensures participants stay engaged throughout the cycle.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2499\" data-end=\"2811\">\n<li data-start=\"2499\" data-end=\"2811\">\n<p data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2811\"><strong data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2512\">Example<\/strong>: A Kenyan events company hosting leadership conferences can use email automation to send a welcome email upon registration, reminder emails one week and one day before the event, and a survey link immediately after. This not only increases attendance but also builds a database for future events.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"53\">Our Email Marketing Process \u2013 From Idea to Inbox<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"55\" data-end=\"319\">Running successful email campaigns isn\u2019t just about having the right tools\u2014it\u2019s about following a structured process. At Aminifu Digital Agency, we use a step-by-step approach that ensures every email we send is relevant, timely, and measurable. Here\u2019s how it works:<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"321\" data-end=\"358\">Discovery and Strategy Workshop<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"482\">We begin by understanding your business objectives and audience. This step ensures your campaigns are built with purpose.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"752\">\n<li data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"752\">\n<p data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"752\"><strong data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"505\">Kenyan use case<\/strong>: A Nairobi-based fintech firm wanted to increase user adoption of their mobile app. In the strategy workshop, we identified customer pain points (trust, usability, onboarding), which guided the creation of a tailored email series for new users.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"754\" data-end=\"799\">List Segmentation and Campaign Planning<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"800\" data-end=\"914\">Next, we segment your subscriber list into meaningful groups. Not all customers should receive the same message.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"1205\">\n<li data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"1205\">\n<p data-start=\"918\" data-end=\"1205\"><strong data-start=\"918\" data-end=\"937\">Kenyan use case<\/strong>: An NGO in Kisumu segmented its list into first-time donors, recurring donors, and corporate sponsors. Each group received a customised communication path\u2014impact stories for first-timers, recognition emails for recurring donors, and detailed reports for corporates.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1207\" data-end=\"1244\">Template Design and Copywriting<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1245\" data-end=\"1453\">Emails are designed to look professional, reflect your brand, and drive action. Copy is crafted to be persuasive, personalised, and mobile-first (critical in Kenya, where most people check email on phones).<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1455\" data-end=\"1682\">\n<li data-start=\"1455\" data-end=\"1682\">\n<p data-start=\"1457\" data-end=\"1682\"><strong data-start=\"1457\" data-end=\"1476\">Kenyan use case<\/strong>: An e-commerce store in Mombasa selling electronics used branded, mobile-optimised templates. Copy was personalised to highlight products based on browsing history, increasing click-throughs by over 25%.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1718\">Automation Setup and Testing<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1719\" data-end=\"1931\">We set up automation workflows that run around the clock. These include welcome sequences, abandoned cart reminders, and lead nurturing campaigns. Before launch, we test every element to ensure smooth delivery.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1933\" data-end=\"2227\">\n<li data-start=\"1933\" data-end=\"2227\">\n<p data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"2227\"><strong data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"1954\">Kenyan use case<\/strong>: A Nairobi training institute used automation for event registrations. Once a participant signed up, they received an immediate confirmation, a reminder one week before, and a follow-up survey after. This sequence boosted attendance rates and captured valuable feedback.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2229\" data-end=\"2250\">Campaign Launch<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2251\" data-end=\"2442\">Once everything is tested and approved, we launch the campaign. We schedule emails at optimal times for maximum engagement, taking into account when Kenyan audiences are most active online.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2444\" data-end=\"2677\">\n<li data-start=\"2444\" data-end=\"2677\">\n<p data-start=\"2446\" data-end=\"2677\"><strong data-start=\"2446\" data-end=\"2465\">Kenyan use case<\/strong>: A supermarket chain ran a weekend promotion campaign. By launching emails early Saturday morning, when customers were planning shopping trips, the campaign saw a sharp spike in foot traffic and online orders.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2679\" data-end=\"2711\">Reporting and Optimisation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2712\" data-end=\"2877\">After launch, we track performance metrics like open rates, click-through rates, and conversions. Based on results, we refine future campaigns for better outcomes.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2879\" data-end=\"3132\">\n<li data-start=\"2879\" data-end=\"3132\">\n<p data-start=\"2881\" data-end=\"3132\"><strong data-start=\"2881\" data-end=\"2900\">Kenyan use case<\/strong>: An education publisher analysed open rates across subject-specific newsletters. They found that teachers engaged more with exam-prep resources than general updates, leading to a strategy shift towards resource-focused campaigns.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Want to build a solid email strategy?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Reach out to us![\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"54\">Why Choose Aminifu Digital Agency for Email Marketing<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"56\" data-end=\"411\">Selecting the right partner for email marketing in Kenya goes beyond technical execution. You need a team that understands the local market, regulatory landscape, and how email integrates with your wider digital ecosystem. Aminifu Digital Agency brings together expertise, creativity, and compl