i data-start=\"2713\" data-end=\"2908\">\n<p data-start=\"2715\" data-end=\"2908\"><strong data-start=\"2715\" data-end=\"2726\">Example<\/strong>: For a retailer, we linked their WooCommerce store with Klaviyo. The integration automated product recommendation emails based on browsing history, increasing average order value.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2910\" data-end=\"2953\">Proven Track Record Across Industries<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2954\" data-end=\"3208\">Our clients range from NGOs seeking donor engagement to corporates managing internal communications and e-commerce brands scaling online sales. Each project demonstrates adaptability to industry-specific needs while maintaining best practice standards.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3210\" data-end=\"3491\">\n<li data-start=\"3210\" data-end=\"3260\">\n<p data-start=\"3212\" data-end=\"3260\">NGOs: Impact-driven storytelling email series.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3261\" data-end=\"3328\">\n<p data-start=\"3263\" data-end=\"3328\">Corporates: Structured communication for clients and employees.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3329\" data-end=\"3412\">\n<p data-start=\"3331\" data-end=\"3412\">E-commerce: Automated cart recovery, product launches, and seasonal promotions.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3413\" data-end=\"3491\">\n<p data-start=\"3415\" data-end=\"3491\">Training providers: Seamless event registration and follow-up automations.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3493\" data-end=\"3691\">Aminifu Digital Agency isn\u2019t just another marketing vendor\u2014we are your growth partner. Our approach blends local insight with global standards, making us the go-to agency for email marketing in Kenya.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Need to improve your email strategy?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&