tart=\"646\" data-end=\"725\">Email 1 (sent 1 hour after abandonment): Gentle reminder with product images.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"810\">\n<p data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"810\">Email 2 (sent 24 hours later): Highlighted urgency (\u201cYour cart is almost gone\u201d).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"811\" data-end=\"890\">\n<p data-start=\"813\" data-end=\"890\">Email 3 (sent 72 hours later): Incentivised checkout with a small discount.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"892\" data-end=\"906\"><strong data-start=\"892\" data-end=\"904\">Results:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"1209\">\n<li data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"983\">\n<p data-start=\"909\" data-end=\"983\"><strong data-start=\"909\" data-end=\"937\">27% of recovered revenue<\/strong> attributed directly to the automation flow.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"984\" data-end=\"1064\">\n<p data-start=\"986\" data-end=\"1064\">Average open rate across the series: <strong data-start=\"1023\" data-end=\"1030\">58%<\/strong> (well above industry averages).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1065\" data-end=\"1111\">\n<p data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1111\">Average click-through rate (CTR): <strong data-start=\"1101\" data-end=\"1108\">18%<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1209\">\n<p data-start=\"1114\" data-end=\"1209\">Customers who recovered carts showed a <strong data-start=\"1153\" data-end=\"1188\">22% higher repeat purchase rate<\/strong> over three months.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1211\" data-end=\"1321\">This campaign demonstrated how automation doesn\u2019t just save lost sales\u2014it builds long-term customer loyalty.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2363\" data-end=\"2432\">EdTech: 41% Higher Webinar Signups With Targeted Drip Campaigns<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2433\" data-end=\"2600\">A Nairobi-based EdTech company offering online courses needed to drive registrations for its webinars. Their single promotional blasts were failing to fill sessions.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2602\" data-end=\"2620\"><strong data-start=\"2602\" data-end=\"2618\">What we did:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2621\" data-end=\"3033\">\n<li data-start=\"2621\" data-end=\"2730\">\n<p data-start=\"2623\" data-end=\"2730\">Built a <strong data-start=\"2631\" data-end=\"2655\">4-part drip campaign<\/strong> targeting different audience segments: educators, students, and parents.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2731\" data-end=\"2816\">\n<p data-start=\"2733\" data-end=\"2816\">Emails provided value first (tips, free resources) before promoting the webinars.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2817\" data-end=\"2933\">\n<p data-start=\"2819\" data-end=\"2933\">Each email contained a clear <strong data-start=\"2848\" data-end=\"2872\">call-to-action (CTA)<\/strong> to register, reinforced by urgency (\u201cSeats filling fast\u201d).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2934\" data-end=\"3033\">\n<p data-start=\"2936\" data-end=\"3033\">Linked the email system with their <strong data-start=\"2971\" data-end=\"2978\">CRM<\/strong> to personalise based on previous webinar attendance.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3035\" data-end=\"3049\"><strong data-start=\"3035\" data-end=\"3047\">Results:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3050\" data-end=\"3399\">\n<li data-start=\"3050\" data-end=\"3123\">\n<p data-start=\"3052\" data-end=\"3123\">Webinar sign-ups increased by <strong data-start=\"3082\" data-end=\"3089\">41%<\/strong> compared to previous campaigns.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3124\" data-end=\"3182\">\n<p data-start=\"3126\" data-end=\"3182\">Open rates averaged <strong data-start=\"3146\" data-end=\"3153\">46%<\/strong>, and CTR stood at <strong data-start=\"3172\" data-end=\"3179\">15%<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3183\" data-end=\"3306\">\n<p data-start=\"3185\" data-end=\"3306\">Post-webinar surveys revealed a <strong data-start=\"3217\" data-end=\"3249\">20% increase in satisfaction<\/strong>, as registrants felt better informed before attending.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3307\" data-end=\"3399\">\n<p data-start=\"3309\" data-end=\"3399\">The client converted <strong data-start=\"3330\" data-end=\"3350\">17% of attendees<\/strong> into paying course subscribers within a month.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3401\" data-end=\"3535\">By combining segmentation, education, and automation, the EdTech brand transformed webinars into a reliable lead-generation channel.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"68\">Ready to Grow With Email Marketing? Let\u2019s Automate Your Success<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"70\" data-end=\"436\">Email marketing is one of the most powerful and cost-effective ways to grow your business in Kenya. Whether you are an SME looking to nurture leads, an NGO aiming to deepen donor relationships, or an e-commerce brand ready to recover lost sales, the opportunity is right in front of you. What you need is a partner who can turn email into a reliable growth engine.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"438\" data-end=\"699\">At Aminifu Digital Agency, we don\u2019t just send emails\u2014we design systems that engage, convert, and retain. With over a decade of experience running digital campaigns in Kenya, we know how to combine strategy, creativity, and technology to deliver measurable impact.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"701\" data-end=\"725\">Take the Next Step<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"1082\">We\u2019re offering a <strong data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"773\">free email marketing audit<\/strong> to show you exactly where you\u2019re leaving opportunities on the table and how automation can unlock growth. Alongside the audit, you\u2019ll receive a <strong data-start=\"918\" data-end=\"951\">sample subject line framework<\/strong> and a <strong data-start=\"958\" data-end=\"985\">starter a